        <para id="id1164316753387"/>
        <para id="id1164318508950">Bonnie en Tommie sê: </para>
        <para id="id1164317729503">Dit is maklik om met 1c -, 2c -, 5c - en 10c - stukke te werk.</para>
        <list id="id1164310641628" list-type="bulleted">
          <item>Wat is die bedrag in die beursie?</item>
        </list>
        <figure id="id1164292935754">
          <media id="id1164292935754_media" alt="">
            <image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/graphics8-8d38.png" id="id1164292935754__onlineimage" height="218" width="575"/>
