        <list id="id1164313652664" list-type="bulleted">
          <item>Skryf die munte wat in hul beursies is se waardes in: (1c, 2c, 5c en 10c)</item>
        </list>
        <figure id="id1164312670324">
          <media id="id1164312670324_media" alt="">
            <image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/graphics9-f67a.png" id="id1164312670324__onlineimage" height="219" width="575"/>
